@startuml 04_sequence_wali_murid_melihat_absensi_anak
title Sequence Diagram - Wali Murid Melihat Absensi Anak
hide footbox
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #2F4F8F
  LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4F8F
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #F8FBFF
  ActorBorderColor #111827
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BoxBorderColor #CBD5E1
  BoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}


actor "Wali Murid" as Wali
boundary "Halaman Sistem" as Halaman
control "Sistem BimbelOrion" as Sistem
database "Database" as Database


Wali -> Halaman: Buka menu Absensi Anak
Halaman -> Sistem: Meminta halaman wali absensi
Sistem -> Sistem: Memastikan hak aksesnya wali_murid
Sistem -> Database: Mengambil data absensi anak berdasarkan wali_id
Database --> Sistem: Mengirim daftar absensi anak
alt Data absensi kosong
  Sistem --> Halaman: Mengirim hasil ke halaman
else Data absensi ada
  Sistem --> Halaman: Mengirim hasil ke halaman
end
Halaman --> Wali: Menampilkan hasil kepada pengguna
@enduml
